          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Disaster Assistance Simplification Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits a recipient of a disaster-recovery&nbsp;grant from the Department of Housing and Urban Development from denying an&nbsp;applicant for assistance, or reducing the amount of assistance offered to the applicant, on the basis that the applicant denied disaster-recovery relief assistance from the Small Business Administration.</p>]]></text>
